snippet.title: Hello Kitty Happy Town Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
This here is a gameplay preview of Hello Kitty Happy Town, a very fun mobile game that young girls will enjoy. 

Visit our blog http://www.playbuzz.org/ for all the info you need about your favorite free game.

You can play this game at http://www.playnook.com. Check out all of the free online games you can choose to play in that site.
